uses server

docs ServerResult
    The result of the factory manager server.

    docs status
        Server exit status message.
    done
done

type ServerResult
    status text
done

docs ServerError
    An error from the factory manager server.

    docs message
        Description of what went wrong.
    done
done

type ServerError
    message text
done

docs main
    Entry point for the Factory Manager web application.
    Starts the HTTP server on port 8080.
done

flow main
    emit result as ServerResult
    fail error as ServerError
body
    step server.Start() then
        next :result to res
        emit res to :result
    done
done
